Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.51,0:00:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空好藍 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.25,0:00:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的一句話使內心相繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.39,0:00:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上鞋子敞開門扉的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.07,0:00:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你重合的景色使我心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.04,0:00:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢\N加速的心跳無法壓抑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.95,0:01:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人共同感受  季節不斷更替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.49,0:01:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的瞬間\N編織著邂逅的物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.40,0:01:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對紛飛的櫻花許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.24,0:01:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.09,0:01:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（#20 擦肩而過的心意）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，上學會遲到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.59,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.49,0:01:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼催我也來得及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.36,0:01:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一樣毫不所動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.30,0:01:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是音夢妳太心急了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為時間會不夠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.77,0:01:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.97,0:01:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起床時不是吻過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是早安的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是出門前的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.02,0:02:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡哥哥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.66,0:02:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是快遲到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.43,0:02:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，一下子就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿妳沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像太幸福了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.02,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，時間變得好趕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都是因為誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.72,0:02:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.93,0:02:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我昨天趕著回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.74,0:02:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.30,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到音夢恢復精神我也安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.91,0:03:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓妳擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.11,0:03:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有生氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會計較這種事情啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.79,0:03:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的哥哥跟音夢走得好近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來感情真是好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然變成這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.73,0:03:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得你們看起來好像情侶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.77,0:03:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你們這麼親密不禁就這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該沒有這回事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.92,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.93,0:03:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，再不快點就遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.53,0:03:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，要不要來我家呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我買到之前偶像劇的DVD了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟哥哥有約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有約？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近妳好少陪我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.73,0:04:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說朝倉兄妹最近\N感情好到有些奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.57,0:04:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杉並，你別胡說八道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.24,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不是那樣的\N-音夢學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有資料要給風紀委員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要我們馬上集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，所以我過來接妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳只是去拿資料吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳快點去吧，我等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我馬上回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.60,0:05:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.17,0:05:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，可以借點時間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.78,0:05:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉早上說了些奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.62,0:05:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼音夢好像是你的女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.86,0:05:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是開玩笑也不能這樣說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們兩人是兄妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得也必須要告訴妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然跟音夢…這是騙人的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼，為什麼是音夢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是你妹妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢是你的妹妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又是為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.56,0:06:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去我一直把她當作是妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.86,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從決定當她哥哥\N之後一直如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來也打算繼續這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你還記得我們的約定嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那三個約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在永不枯萎的櫻花樹下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.29,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥曾經跟我約定過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.79,0:07:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得去美國了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後就見不到小櫻桃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為變成這樣所以我想說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我對哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.91,0:07:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.75,0:07:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，說清楚啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻桃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.39,0:07:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你願意跟我約定嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.20,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一個約定是一定要重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.07,0:08:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二個約定是\N在我碰到困難時要幫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼還有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得第三個約定嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.86,0:08:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠再度重逢\N到時就要當我的戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N我還以為你忘記了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.44,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥遵守第一個約定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也能遵守第三個約定嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.82,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不說話呢，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定我當然還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在的我對音夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.73,0:08:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.84,0:09:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是別人我就會原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.61,0:09:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要哥哥真的喜歡那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也會死心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我就是不要音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你會遵守第三個約定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會當我的男朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不回答我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.01,0:09:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我就不可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.02,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.89,0:09:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，只有音夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢妳太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.74,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想同時得到哥哥跟男朋友\N實在是太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明知道我的心意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻也很過份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.42,0:10:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道小櫻喜歡哥哥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.92,0:10:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像小櫻知道我的心意一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是因為知道我的心意\N才跟哥哥做了三個約定對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天妳其實知道我躲在樹蔭下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我對哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.94,0:10:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，說清楚啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻桃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.82,0:11:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你願意跟我約定嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.60,0:11:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那棵櫻樹下所作的約定\N一定會實現對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.34,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以小櫻明明知道我在場\N還是訂下了那些約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.47,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真正過份的人是小櫻妳吧\N-才不是那個樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.31,0:11:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在美國的時候\N音夢一直跟哥哥在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此竟然還說\N以後也要永遠在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳太貪心了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想跟哥哥在一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻也可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.89,0:11:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能住在哥哥家裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能跟哥哥一起生活嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.49,0:11:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢因為是妹妹\N所以能永遠陪著哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.97,0:11:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想當一個妹妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳，音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡哥哥，我一直在等他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-所以…\N-不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個我不答應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等的不只是小櫻而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-音夢\N-別再吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看見妳們兩人這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是音夢她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了，小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.92,0:12:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.89,0:12:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻她哭了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻她怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我不對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對的應該是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你覺得我做錯了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，真的不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.57,0:13:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們果然還是不能當情侶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「沒有這回事」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然說不出這句話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.17,0:14:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.54,0:14:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.89,0:14:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意不會改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓給音夢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個我不想讓步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.67,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不能讓步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的是音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.10,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我進來囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.17,0:15:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.61,0:15:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉很難看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是兄妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.82,0:15:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還是不應該這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何，我還是對哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想離開妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.87,0:15:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後也永遠陪著我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠都在我的懷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.96,0:16:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.49,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.02,0:16:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉小櫻，我們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再跟我道歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.12,0:16:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好像是你很可憐一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.56,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再為難哥哥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，音夢她昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.80,0:16:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢的口中掉出櫻花的花瓣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.77,0:16:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳音夢，快點醒來啊\N（#21  小櫻的決心）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.99,0:17:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒐集心的碎片  想趕快送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.63,0:17:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎快要滿溢  真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.37,0:17:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人漫步於鈴音輕響的樹蔭下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.98,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合而為一的影子\N高興地凝視著夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花之雨紛飛著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.06,0:17:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由樹梢陽光所籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.76,0:17:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在累積於胸口的哀傷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.21,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更替的季節與不變的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.41,0:18:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會演奏通往未來的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.66,0:18:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛總是能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有看到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個怎麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.71,0:18:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說是怎麼樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.98,0:18:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個很好的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.15,0:18:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在烏龍麵店吃烏龍涼麵喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏龍涼麵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是個普通人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢，完全不像個普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊也看到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是長什麼樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是這樣的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長這個樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得好像沒有尾巴耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.70,0:19:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就是怪獸了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像會把我們吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.44,0:19:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我個人倒是很有自信的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這邊不覺得很像嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.95,0:19:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會像的話也太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如大家一起找出那個人如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他應該會在島上某處才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這或許不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也讚成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.67,0:20:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先把目標命名為\N「不可思議先生」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的就是發現跟捕獲他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用捕獲這種說法不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.61,0:20:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只要找到就通知大家\N然後再確認他的去處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.39,0:20:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人有門禁時間\N時間限制就設為六點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.16,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.99,0:20:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看過不可思議先生的人\N只有我、白河同學及水越學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就兩人一組分成三組去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.34,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready GO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GO GO GO GO GO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去那邊看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，他不會在那種地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.20,0:21:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在想裡面可能會有\N小一號的不可思議先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.74,0:21:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看，有一個10圓硬幣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.48,0:21:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是在找這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.75,0:21:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有出現呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.55,0:21:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.97,0:21:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.52,0:22:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎，姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要六點了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了，我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.55,0:22:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.45,0:22:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了，他在港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.32,0:23:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議先生～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.67,0:23:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來真的有這個人呢
